com.google.gcloud.datastore

Class ProjectionEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gcloud.datastore.ProjectionEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class ProjectionEntity
extends Object
    A projection entity is a result of a Google Cloud Datastore projection query. A projection entity holds one or more properties, represented by a name (as String) and a value (as Value), and may have a Key.
    See Also:
    Google Cloud Datastore projection queries, Google Cloud Datastore Entities, Properties, and Keys, Serialized Form
